&nbsp;
"Maybe Russia will give up a lot, maybe not." US President Donald Trump said this during a press conference with Indian Prime Minister Narendra Modi, to ask what Russia will have to give up in negotiations to reach an agreement with Ukraine.&nbsp;
"It's too early to say how the negotiations will go," Trump said. Russia "conquered a fairly large portion of territory, perhaps it will renounce to much or perhaps not, the <a href="https://www.agi.it/estero/news/2025-02-13/ucraine-negotiators-trump-putin-30004415/">negotiated is not yet started</a>, but I believe it will be possible to find an agreement", he reiterated.&n.

